thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Lucien Morand

author: Lucien Morand
title: Lucien Morand
text:
It was the first time i rented a vehicule with Omega, and i was pleasantly surprised by the service.I arrived outside working hours and Omega arranged for me to retrieve the car at the Ride and Park and i was able to leave it in town . I will come back .
Thank you .
Lucien
